PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Finance of James Grant Matkin, of Vancouver, British Columbia, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Bank of Canada for a term of three years, effective March 1, 1992, in the place of Leslie Murray Little, whose term will expire.
